    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Wood impregnated with thermosetting resin then subjected to heat and pressure to provide both resin curing and compression.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
